## SOC-Lite Triage Tool

- Built a Python-based SOC triage tool for analyzing Windows, Linux, and Splunk-style CSV logs
- Detects failed login spikes, suspicious PowerShell/cmd activity, privileged activity, and public IP logins
- Maps alerts to MITRE ATT&CK techniques and generates Markdown + JSON reports
- Tools: Python, CSV logs, MITRE ATT&CK, SOC Triage, Incident Response
** To Run:** python soc_lite.py --input sample_logs/auth_events.csv --output reports/triage_report.md
